## Scope
Financial Hotpath #6 (micro-gate INSERT logic) — UPDATE→NEW detection guard. When an extractor re-posts a signal for a ticker that already has an ACTIVE/PENDING/PARTIALLY_CLOSED position from the same trader AND the entry price is within ±5% of the existing position, suppress the phantom INSERT and log `A7_UPDATE_DETECTED` quarantine + `UPDATE_DETECTED` event. >5% difference falls through to INSERT with a notes annotation.

